moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場絶大部份長者嘅話題都係話支持年輕人 ，<br />\n話佢哋好叻，付出咗好多， 話自己無用，<br />\n叫佢哋留返條命。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿途啲嬸嬸全部大鬧警察。</blockquote>好多人都話有， 叫佢留番畀有需要嘅人 ，叫佢哋畀黃店， 叫佢哋唔好畀藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n啲長者叫佢哋自己都要留返啲， 話唔知個疫情去到幾時。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1054d54194925938471fd2440c43d983d50a3fd","tid":1876321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:59:14.000Z","msg":"結果搞到啲錢跌咗喺地下， 個嬸嬸就走咗，我叫年輕人收咗佢， 擋佢哋要買物資。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我看見民心。"},{"pid":"944363a5c0ed120213e590e92971191df1748e43","tid":1876321,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa709367f3bf62f4b970f4c2f03aabac0e6a96c","tid":1876321,"uid":252528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55042588038e59b7a171d880dbd6a8cf73deb744","tid":1876321,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"多謝銀髮手足"},{"pid":"3e74c2e1182d91709a013b8a4e8b9ea783c97559","tid":1876321,"uid":116052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"喺屋企家居隔離緊？<br />\n無口罩出唔到街？<br />\n喺街排緊隊買口罩？<br />\n咁快啲過嚟Twitter戰線！<br />\n<br />\n要光復香港撳幾個掣都唔得？<br />\nTwitterHelpBot嘅tasklist 24小時更新<br />\n入去 <a hre